            <div class="row issue-teaser">
             <div class="issue-image col-xs-3 col-md-4">
              <img alt="University Seal" src="https://provost.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/square_small/public/images/issues/teasers/university.seal_.rgb_.maroon.jpg?itok=Iw4_wyca&amp;c=3b96134e67f62adea3a841e224b5ee14" title="University Seal" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
             </div>
             <div class="issue-title col-xs-9 col-md-8">
              <h4>
               Discrimination, Harassment, and Sexual Misconduct
              </h4>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
             <div class="issue-summary col-xs-12">
              <p>
               The Office of the Provost oversees the University’s efforts to prevent, correct, and where indicated, discipline unlawful discrimination, harassment, and sexual misconduct.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </a>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-list-item">
           <a href="/issues/teaching-and-research">
            <div class="row issue-teaser">
             <div class="issue-image col-xs-3 col-md-4">
              <img alt="Teaching and Research" src="https://provost.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/square_small/public/images/issues/teasers/20141115_MellonMays_8521.JPG?itok=sYyvTVdA&amp;c=c22ad154e6066e545ee234106c292af3" title="Teaching and Research" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
             </div>
             <div class="issue-title col-xs-9 col-md-8">
              <h4>
               Teaching and Research
              </h4>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
             <div class="issue-summary col-xs-12">
              <p>
               In working closely with faculty members and other scholars, the Office of the Provost identifies opportunities to enrich the academic experience and ensure a unique and supportive intellectual environment.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </a>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-list-item">
           <a href="/issues/uchicagograd">
            <div class="row issue-teaser">
             <div class="issue-image col-xs-3 col-md-4">
              <img alt="UChicagoGRAD" src="https://provost.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/square_small/public/images/issues/teasers/garg.jpg?itok=wpoI_zxS&amp;c=5dccf87e9aedc60191b160da4aec1a55" title="UChicagoGRAD" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
             </div>
             <div class="issue-title col-xs-9 col-md-8">
              <h4>
               UChicagoGRAD
              </h4>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
             <div class="issue-summary col-xs-12">
              <p>
               UChicagoGRAD supports the University's more than 9,000 graduate students and postdocs in building the skills they need to become the next generation of leaders.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </a>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-list-item">
           <a href="/issues/uchicago-urban">
            <div class="row issue-teaser">
             <div class="issue-image col-xs-3 col-md-4">
              <img alt="Urban" src="https://provost.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/square_small/public/images/issues/teasers/20140721_Neighborhoods_1030-bright.jpg?itok=rECStO-G&amp;c=b2dbd6da32fefa8f8393574d891dc1fe" title="Urban" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
             </div>
             <div class="issue-title col-xs-9 col-md-8">
              <h4>
               UChicago Urban
              </h4>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
             <div class="issue-summary col-xs-12">
              <p>
               The Office of the Provost works to support research dedicated to improving urban life, implementing the most promising policies and programs around the world.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </a>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-list-item">
           <a href="/issues/planning-and-support">
            <div class="row issue-teaser">
             <div class="issue-image col-xs-3 col-md-4">
              <img src="https://provost.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/square_small/public/images/issues/teasers/admin_circle.jpg?itok=9WadlWAW&amp;c=12a8810072c91cd32801e25290125283" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
             </div>
             <div class="issue-title col-xs-9 col-md-8">
              <h4>
               Planning and Support
              </h4>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
             <div class="issue-summary col-xs-12">
              <p>
               The Office of the Provost supports deans, department chairs, faculty members, and other scholars through the allocation of funds, space, and resources.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </a>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
